data.title: Fisher Announces Fall 2022 Dean’s List Honorees - St. John Fisher University
data.text:
Fisher Announces Fall 2023 Dean’s List Honorees

St. John Fisher University recently announced the Dean’s List honorees for the Fall 2023 semester, which includes more than 1,400 undergraduate students.

To be eligible for the Dean’s List, a student must have attained at least a 3.5 grade-point average for the semester.

“This achievement clearly recognizes the excellent academic performance of our students and is a tribute to their dedication to their studies,” said Dr. Kevin Railey, provost of the University.
